description:
Hello, we  are maishinta👪 We are Japanese artists.🇯🇵 We create music🎶, drawings🎨, and many other kinds of creations.

These works are 8-bit dots of a gentle smiling face that maishinta has been working on for more than 6 years.
This collection will be 111 pieces in total.

HOHOEMI is the Japanese word for a gentle smile☺️

We create these works with the hope that the world will be filled with HOHOEMI.

The title of the first music produced by maishinta is also HOHOEMI.

We will continue to expand the world of HOHOEMI through artistic expression.

maishinta
name: HOHOEMI PEOPLE
